WEBVTT

00:18.560 --> 00:23.430
[Zhizi Alley]

00:27.670 --> 00:28.760
What are we eating tonight?

00:28.760 --> 00:30.320
Bin, you're still thinking about food?

00:30.320 --> 00:31.280
Look at how fat you are.

00:31.280 --> 00:32.670
Your fat jiggles when you walk.

00:32.670 --> 00:32.960
No,

00:32.960 --> 00:34.280
I'm starving.

00:34.350 --> 00:36.110
Finish what's in your mouth first,

00:36.110 --> 00:37.600
then look at your big belly.

00:37.600 --> 00:39.070
All he's thinking about
is that he's hungry,

00:39.070 --> 00:39.920
you know?

00:40.110 --> 00:41.240
Alright, that's enough.

00:41.240 --> 00:42.920
It's quite bouncy, though.

00:58.000 --> 00:58.930
Jiang Hansheng,

00:59.280 --> 01:00.150
hurry up!

01:01.470 --> 01:03.670
Why are you always so slow?

01:19.640 --> 01:20.590
Jiang Hansheng!

01:20.950 --> 01:22.150
Hurry up!

01:23.840 --> 01:24.560
What are you looking at?

01:24.560 --> 01:25.950
This is no longer your home.

01:25.950 --> 01:27.120
The car has been waiting outside
for a long time.

01:27.120 --> 01:27.950
Let's go.

01:32.070 --> 01:33.670
Say hello to Auntie Xiaoruo.

01:33.850 --> 01:35.009
Hello, Hansheng.

01:35.430 --> 01:36.360
Say hello to her.

01:36.430 --> 01:37.030
It's fine.

01:37.479 --> 01:38.280
This child...

01:38.570 --> 01:39.650
It's okay. We can

01:39.860 --> 01:40.740
talk in the car.

01:41.050 --> 01:42.220
Let's go. Hurry.

01:43.280 --> 01:44.039
Bozhi.

01:44.640 --> 01:45.280
Let's go!

01:46.220 --> 01:47.350
I don't want to move.

01:50.550 --> 01:51.500
Hansheng,

01:52.220 --> 01:53.620
this house has been sold.

01:53.630 --> 01:54.840
You have to move.

01:54.840 --> 01:55.789
Can't you buy it back?

01:55.789 --> 01:57.759
You know my new company

01:57.759 --> 01:58.710
is far from here.

01:58.920 --> 02:00.310
When Xiaoruo and I come back at night,

02:00.310 --> 02:01.750
there's no place to park.

02:01.780 --> 02:02.590
We're moving to a

02:02.590 --> 02:04.280
bigger and better place, right?

02:04.280 --> 02:05.440
Let's go. Hurry up.

02:06.440 --> 02:07.440
I don't want to go.

02:10.560 --> 02:11.520
Jiang Hansheng,

02:11.960 --> 02:13.440
before you turn 18,

02:13.440 --> 02:14.630
I have an obligation to raise you.

02:14.630 --> 02:15.790
When you turn 18

02:15.790 --> 02:16.990
and you're a grownup,

02:17.000 --> 02:17.720
where you want to live

02:17.720 --> 02:18.870
and who you want to be with

02:18.870 --> 02:19.870
will no longer be my business.

02:19.870 --> 02:21.220
So you have to come with me now.

02:21.220 --> 02:21.750
Let's go.

02:23.100 --> 02:23.440
Okay, okay.

02:23.440 --> 02:24.160
What's wrong with you?

02:24.160 --> 02:24.750
Okay, okay.

02:24.750 --> 02:26.560
Don't be angry. Let me talk to him.

02:26.560 --> 02:27.240
Hansheng,

02:27.590 --> 02:28.840
just come with us.

02:29.350 --> 02:30.440
We will be

02:30.440 --> 02:31.720
a family from now on, right?

02:31.720 --> 02:32.790
Living together,

02:32.820 --> 02:33.750
we can take care of each other.

02:33.750 --> 02:34.940
I'm used to living alone.

02:34.940 --> 02:36.740
I don't like being taken care of.

02:36.960 --> 02:39.240
You're used to living alone
and don't like being taken care of?

02:39.240 --> 02:40.590
You think you're all grown up now, huh?

02:40.590 --> 02:41.120
Fine.

02:41.150 --> 02:42.640
You can live here alone.

02:42.660 --> 02:44.190
Let's see if you can stay until next month

02:44.190 --> 02:46.120
without being kicked out by the new owner.

02:46.120 --> 02:46.790
Okay?

02:47.490 --> 02:48.630
Let's go. He won't go, but we will.

02:48.630 --> 02:49.590
Let's go.

02:50.210 --> 02:51.170
Hurry. Let's go.

02:51.350 --> 02:52.280
Leave him alone.

02:52.790 --> 02:53.960
This child...

03:13.240 --> 03:14.570
You're covered in rain.

03:15.960 --> 03:16.790
Slow down.

03:17.400 --> 03:18.400
There's a puddle.

04:50.800 --> 04:56.390
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

04:56.750 --> 04:59.190
[Episode 17]

05:19.420 --> 05:19.980
Dahua.

05:20.220 --> 05:21.340
Pack up, let's go.

05:21.980 --> 05:23.310
We're finally leaving.

06:04.070 --> 06:05.200
Still the old rules.

06:19.780 --> 06:21.040
What's the situation?

06:27.930 --> 06:29.710
If you don't want me to end up like Yao,

06:29.710 --> 06:31.770
clear out the mole in your team first.

06:32.350 --> 06:33.000
Chief Tan,

06:33.630 --> 06:34.920
your previous suspicions

06:34.920 --> 06:36.159
have been confirmed.

06:37.000 --> 06:39.310
Jiang Cheng knows
our one-way contact method.

06:39.310 --> 06:40.360
After we met,

06:40.750 --> 06:41.680
he didn't make any

06:41.680 --> 06:42.830
moves against us.

06:43.270 --> 06:44.930
He told us to search for moles.

06:45.510 --> 06:46.770
He really is Cangfeng.

06:47.310 --> 06:48.830
If he really is Cangfeng,

06:49.720 --> 06:51.720
why did he use this rare opportunity

06:52.040 --> 06:53.870
to only leave this one sentence?

06:56.159 --> 06:57.240
He saw Zhou Jin,

06:57.510 --> 06:59.420
and that's why he was willing to say this.

06:59.420 --> 07:00.350
Among everyone,

07:00.390 --> 07:02.250
the one he trusts the most
must be Zhou Jin.

07:02.250 --> 07:04.710
If it were someone else
in front of him today,

07:04.800 --> 07:07.130
he probably wouldn't even have said that.

07:09.680 --> 07:11.010
They dare to deal drugs,

07:11.560 --> 07:13.680
which means their situation
is basically stable.

07:13.680 --> 07:15.540
They have reason to be confident.

07:15.800 --> 07:17.660
Let's not break this confidence.

07:18.190 --> 07:19.570
Once we alert the opponent,

07:19.570 --> 07:21.030
variables will multiply,

07:21.110 --> 07:23.640
and it will only increase
our own difficulty.

07:25.070 --> 07:27.000
We need to find the internal crack,

07:27.160 --> 07:29.090
but we can't completely fill it in.

07:29.270 --> 07:30.630
We still need to leave him

07:30.630 --> 07:32.750
time and space to contact the outside,

07:32.750 --> 07:35.080
creating an illusion of going unnoticed.

07:35.159 --> 07:35.890
We could even

07:36.270 --> 07:37.560
use this person

07:37.830 --> 07:39.480
to pass information in reverse

07:39.480 --> 07:40.480
and confuse them.

07:42.210 --> 07:43.570
Professor Jiang,

07:44.040 --> 07:45.830
your idea is good,

07:47.190 --> 07:49.320
but the problem is how to implement it.

07:50.530 --> 07:52.260
And if we don't find the mole,

07:52.820 --> 07:54.240
how can we make Jiang Cheng believe

07:54.240 --> 07:55.700
that we found this person?

07:55.920 --> 07:57.780
Won't it threaten his operation?

07:59.040 --> 07:59.900
That's an idea.

08:00.750 --> 08:02.480
We need to let Jiang Cheng know.

08:07.160 --> 08:08.620
-How about this?
-Mentor.

08:23.040 --> 08:24.160
This should work.

08:26.430 --> 08:27.030
Chief Tan,

08:28.270 --> 08:29.750
how much have you narrowed down

08:29.750 --> 08:31.280
your previous suspicions?

08:34.840 --> 08:36.100
The ones who first knew

08:36.679 --> 08:39.480
that Leader Yao
personally participated in the operation

08:39.480 --> 08:40.679
are mainly these few.

08:43.400 --> 08:46.090
[Liu Liang]

08:46.540 --> 08:47.450
[Lu Pengfei]

08:49.650 --> 08:50.590
[Zhao Ping]

08:51.270 --> 08:52.270
These few people.

08:56.120 --> 08:56.550
Also,

08:57.820 --> 08:59.880
Professor Jiang, didn't you undergo

09:00.000 --> 09:01.910
the investigation team's interrogation?

09:01.910 --> 09:03.360
Now, I can tell you

09:04.390 --> 09:06.750
this interrogation was jointly planned

09:08.600 --> 09:10.170
with my superiors.

09:10.440 --> 09:11.960
The main purpose was to evaluate

09:11.960 --> 09:14.150
all those who participated
in the operation.

09:14.150 --> 09:14.870
But

09:16.790 --> 09:18.650
the results were disappointing.

09:20.000 --> 09:22.150
The problem is right beside us.

09:22.960 --> 09:23.690
Understood.

09:24.360 --> 09:26.080
Since there was an interrogation,

09:26.080 --> 09:27.440
it can be considered that

09:27.440 --> 09:28.440
personality tests

09:28.440 --> 09:31.030
and observations of speech and behavior
have already been done.

09:31.030 --> 09:32.490
Then we can go ahead and use

09:32.550 --> 09:33.790
a fake case

09:34.240 --> 09:35.870
to force the mole to show up.

09:36.550 --> 09:37.750
A fake case?

09:40.000 --> 09:40.870
Fabricate

09:40.960 --> 09:42.630
an operation against Old Scorpion.

09:42.630 --> 09:44.690
An absolutely successful operation

09:44.970 --> 09:46.380
to make him panic.

09:49.590 --> 09:50.190
Chief Tan.

09:50.720 --> 09:51.870
Besides Zhou Jin,

09:52.270 --> 09:53.870
who else in the Nancheng Branch

09:53.870 --> 09:55.070
do you trust the most?

09:57.870 --> 09:58.480
Wan.

09:59.320 --> 10:00.200
Wan Chongshan.

10:00.670 --> 10:02.000
He is absolutely clean.

10:02.440 --> 10:02.870
Okay.

10:03.510 --> 10:04.310
Then I suggest

10:04.510 --> 10:05.480
you, Zhou Jin,

10:05.670 --> 10:06.630
and Wan Chongshan

10:06.630 --> 10:08.030
lead three teams separately

10:08.030 --> 10:09.360
and act independently.

10:09.600 --> 10:11.450
At the beginning of the operation,

10:11.450 --> 10:12.980
when he's still in the dark,

10:13.390 --> 10:15.790
cut off his chances
to contact the outside.

10:15.910 --> 10:17.370
Separate the three people

10:17.370 --> 10:18.870
and, in three different places,

10:18.870 --> 10:21.440
each successfully bust
Old Scorpion's drug deal.

10:21.440 --> 10:22.440
Before and after,

10:22.670 --> 10:23.670
they must report,

10:23.670 --> 10:24.390
ask,

10:24.720 --> 10:25.670
and confirm.

10:28.390 --> 10:29.030
Finally,

10:30.180 --> 10:31.510
the ideal situation will be

10:31.510 --> 10:34.560
that Old Scorpion's side will
get a set of information.

10:34.560 --> 10:36.360
As long as Jiang Cheng knows,
he will understand

10:36.360 --> 10:37.600
that it's our doing.

10:38.320 --> 10:39.080
But he might not know

10:39.080 --> 10:40.080
what we are doing,

10:40.630 --> 10:42.030
so he will be anxious too.

10:43.080 --> 10:44.120
Normally,

10:44.630 --> 10:46.430
he will contact us proactively.

10:46.790 --> 10:49.200
We can use Jiang Cheng's feedback

10:49.730 --> 10:50.930
to lock onto the mole.

10:51.960 --> 10:52.790
Three cars

10:53.260 --> 10:56.260
going to three places
to catch three groups of people.

10:56.270 --> 10:57.140
Whichever car's information

10:57.140 --> 10:58.660
gets to Old Scorpion,

10:59.120 --> 11:00.030
that car

11:00.420 --> 11:01.680
will have the suspect.

11:03.000 --> 11:03.630
But

11:04.080 --> 11:05.940
we'll need Jiang Cheng to tell us.

11:06.120 --> 11:07.150
The problem is...

11:08.790 --> 11:11.320
Can he have
such tacit understanding with us?

11:12.720 --> 11:13.510
If not,

11:14.320 --> 11:16.380
either his ability is questionable,

11:16.440 --> 11:18.170
or his stance is questionable.

11:18.870 --> 11:19.870
This is also a test

11:20.510 --> 11:22.570
of whether Jiang Cheng is on our side.

11:26.440 --> 11:27.040
Chief Tan.

11:27.720 --> 11:28.360
I suggest

11:28.870 --> 11:31.080
everyone participates in this operation.

11:31.080 --> 11:32.360
In this operation,

11:32.840 --> 11:35.000
don't let the mole feel targeted.

11:36.600 --> 11:37.660
Not only this time.

11:38.480 --> 11:39.810
Don't touch this person

11:40.120 --> 11:41.650
until we can close the case.

11:42.200 --> 11:44.000
He might be useful in the future.

11:45.200 --> 11:46.030
I understand.

11:47.550 --> 11:49.350
As long as we figure out who it is,

11:50.270 --> 11:51.930
we'll just guard against him.

12:32.420 --> 12:34.250
The following meeting
will contain classified information.

12:34.250 --> 12:35.390
Everyone, hand in your phones.

12:35.390 --> 12:36.990
You can turn off your phones.

12:45.840 --> 12:47.370
Let me make introductions.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.720
This is the SWAT team's

12:49.840 --> 12:51.100
Deputy Captain Huang.

12:51.550 --> 12:53.350
From the evening into the night,

12:53.790 --> 12:55.240
we and the SWAT team

12:55.750 --> 12:56.960
might have

12:57.540 --> 12:59.270
an emergency joint operation.

12:59.510 --> 13:00.790
I said "might have"

13:01.030 --> 13:02.790
because the current informant's report

13:02.790 --> 13:04.050
is still unconfirmed.

13:04.080 --> 13:05.840
According to our intelligence,

13:05.840 --> 13:06.630
there is

13:07.150 --> 13:09.910
an impending illegal transaction
in Haizhou,

13:10.150 --> 13:11.810
most likely involving drugs.

13:12.000 --> 13:14.200
As for whether it's related to
the previous case,

13:14.200 --> 13:15.330
we can't be sure yet.

13:15.600 --> 13:17.440
So, given our branch's understanding

13:17.440 --> 13:19.910
of Old Scorpion crime syndicate,

13:20.270 --> 13:21.070
our superiors

13:21.240 --> 13:22.240
ordered us

13:22.240 --> 13:24.770
to participate
in this emergency operation.

13:24.790 --> 13:26.870
At the same time, we might also get some

13:26.870 --> 13:28.330
leads about the suspects.

13:30.080 --> 13:30.910
Okay, here,

13:31.080 --> 13:32.750
I want to emphasize something.

13:32.750 --> 13:33.750
From now on,

13:34.630 --> 13:35.760
everything you hear

13:35.960 --> 13:36.750
and see

13:36.960 --> 13:37.960
is confidential.

13:38.150 --> 13:39.480
Strictly no disclosing

13:39.480 --> 13:40.790
or leaking information.

13:40.790 --> 13:41.510
Understood?

13:41.510 --> 13:42.390
-Understood!
-Understood!

13:42.390 --> 13:42.960
Good.

13:43.440 --> 13:44.150
Next,

13:44.480 --> 13:45.600
Deputy Captain Huang

13:45.600 --> 13:48.530
will brief everyone
on the operational deployment.

13:49.550 --> 13:50.550
Hello, everyone.

13:50.600 --> 13:51.670
I am Huang Weixin.

13:52.630 --> 13:54.630
Tonight's emergency joint operation

13:54.630 --> 13:56.120
is under my command.

13:56.510 --> 13:58.970
First, I'll divide the 12 of you
into groups.

14:13.700 --> 14:14.830
I don't know you all.

14:15.030 --> 14:17.430
Please say "here"
when your name is called.

14:19.870 --> 14:20.470
Group One.

14:21.000 --> 14:22.270
-Lu Pengfei.
-Here.

14:22.850 --> 14:24.210
-Qi Jiayuan.
-Here.

14:24.540 --> 14:25.740
-Li Lei.
-Here.

14:26.180 --> 14:27.840
You three take car number one.

14:27.960 --> 14:28.960
Professor Jiang.

14:29.870 --> 14:31.270
Group Two. Wan Chongshan.

14:31.270 --> 14:32.080
How is it?

14:32.240 --> 14:33.300
-Liu Liang.
-Here.

14:33.510 --> 14:34.790
-Zhang Huilin.
-Here.

14:35.090 --> 14:36.210
-Fang Zhe.
-Here.

14:36.670 --> 14:37.400
Group Three.

14:37.570 --> 14:38.730
-Zhou Jin.
-Here.

14:39.090 --> 14:40.380
-Zhao Ping.
-Here.

14:40.630 --> 14:41.870
-Hu Yuejun.
-Here.

14:42.030 --> 14:43.200
-He Jia.
-Here.

14:45.280 --> 14:45.880
Everyone,

14:46.550 --> 14:48.480
the exact time of this transaction

14:48.600 --> 14:49.670
is 8 P.M. tonight.

14:50.750 --> 14:52.030
This arrest operation

14:52.320 --> 14:53.870
can now be officially declared

14:53.870 --> 14:54.800
to have started.

14:55.750 --> 14:56.630
The transaction location

14:56.630 --> 14:58.290
has been roughly determined.

14:58.600 --> 15:01.530
The specific location
is still being further confirmed.

15:01.530 --> 15:02.730
We have some distance

15:02.870 --> 15:04.000
to our destination.

15:04.150 --> 15:06.960
The cars are downstairs.
Later, we'll get in the cars first.

15:06.960 --> 15:08.390
The specific operation requirements

15:08.390 --> 15:09.920
will be assigned on the way.

15:10.160 --> 15:11.060
The leaders of each group

15:11.060 --> 15:12.650
will also explain it to you in detail.

15:12.650 --> 15:13.280
Understood?

15:13.280 --> 15:14.150
-Understood!
-Understood!

15:14.150 --> 15:14.600
Good.

15:14.750 --> 15:16.510
If you have any questions,
you can ask now.

15:16.510 --> 15:17.510
I have a question.

15:17.720 --> 15:21.250
Is the transaction
related to Old Scorpion's crime syndicate?

15:21.380 --> 15:22.330
We presume so.

15:22.910 --> 15:25.210
How dare they still
traffic drugs at this time?

15:25.210 --> 15:26.700
All our leads have gone cold.

15:26.700 --> 15:28.360
What's the source of this tip?

15:31.150 --> 15:32.110
Regarding this,

15:32.270 --> 15:33.480
I can't tell you now.

15:38.850 --> 15:40.380
The arrest needs to be fast.

15:40.600 --> 15:41.840
There can be no casualties.

15:41.840 --> 15:43.500
The process is not important.

15:44.030 --> 15:45.560
What matters is the result.

15:46.030 --> 15:46.960
The process?

15:47.720 --> 15:49.380
The process is not important.

15:51.250 --> 15:52.890
What matters is the result.

15:54.630 --> 15:55.630
Is everyone here?

15:56.240 --> 15:57.970
Synchronize your watches now.

16:00.200 --> 16:01.000
5:20.

16:01.240 --> 16:02.570
We leave in two minutes.

16:02.780 --> 16:03.660
-Yes.
-Yes.

16:04.510 --> 16:06.310
Sir, I need to use the restroom.

16:08.550 --> 16:09.150
Hurry up.

16:10.030 --> 16:11.090
Anyone who needs to go, go now!

16:11.090 --> 16:11.690
Sir,

16:12.270 --> 16:13.200
then I'll go too.

16:13.720 --> 16:14.320
Go.

16:15.550 --> 16:17.210
Everyone else, get in the car!

16:42.830 --> 16:44.760
This time is mainly to test the waters.

16:44.760 --> 16:45.600
Be careful.

16:45.960 --> 16:47.420
Understood. Don't worry.

17:00.030 --> 17:02.000
Cheng is indeed a talent.

17:02.910 --> 17:05.270
No matter where he goes or what he does,

17:05.720 --> 17:07.960
he adapts quickly and well.

17:27.750 --> 17:29.750
Can you open the window? It's stuffy.

17:29.750 --> 17:31.410
Yeah, you're suffocating us.

17:51.400 --> 17:53.070
Attention, Group Three.

17:53.610 --> 17:55.370
Target location newly confirmed.

17:55.370 --> 17:57.480
South side of Taidong Bridge
in Luotang Town.

17:57.480 --> 17:59.720
South side of Taidong Bridge
in Luotang Town.

17:59.720 --> 18:00.750
South side of Taidong Bridge

18:00.750 --> 18:02.110
in Luotang Town.

18:02.240 --> 18:04.310
Attention,
Nancheng Criminal Investigation units.

18:04.310 --> 18:07.270
Follow the SWAT leader's arrangements
for the arrest.

18:07.270 --> 18:09.510
The main arrest force is the SWAT team.

18:09.660 --> 18:11.830
Barring accidents,
you are mainly responsible for

18:11.830 --> 18:13.750
the post-arrest scene investigation,

18:13.750 --> 18:15.550
and evidence collection
and identification.

18:15.550 --> 18:16.510
Follow their orders.

18:16.510 --> 18:17.160
Copy that.

18:19.510 --> 18:20.160
Senior,

18:20.720 --> 18:22.720
do you know any inside information?

18:23.880 --> 18:24.640
I don't know.

18:28.270 --> 18:29.870
Where did the car in front go?

19:19.310 --> 19:20.440
I'm going.

19:27.480 --> 19:28.110
Go ahead.

19:55.000 --> 19:56.400
Move, fast!

19:57.270 --> 19:58.030
Stop! Don't move!

19:58.030 --> 19:58.720
Stop!

19:59.400 --> 20:00.070
Stop!

20:00.100 --> 20:00.740
Stop!

20:00.760 --> 20:01.440
Stop!

20:04.690 --> 20:05.510
Freeze!

20:08.640 --> 20:09.310
Don't move!

20:10.350 --> 20:11.350
Do you know He Wu?

20:12.110 --> 20:12.790
No.

20:13.030 --> 20:14.960
Think carefully before you speak!

20:14.960 --> 20:15.690
He's my boss.

20:17.100 --> 20:18.880
Have you seen these people before?

20:18.880 --> 20:19.590
No.

20:19.880 --> 20:20.740
Take them away!

20:55.480 --> 20:57.280
Claim your own phones.

21:08.070 --> 21:08.850
I'll head off first.

21:08.850 --> 21:10.880
Something came up at home. I must go back.

21:10.880 --> 21:11.920
Did you tell Chief Tan?

21:11.920 --> 21:13.250
I'll tell him right now.

21:19.400 --> 21:20.030
Junior,

21:20.240 --> 21:21.770
where did you guys go today?

21:22.980 --> 21:24.590
The leaders specifically ordered

21:24.590 --> 21:25.880
that before the interrogation results
are out,

21:25.880 --> 21:27.750
we're not allowed to
talk about this in private.

21:27.750 --> 21:29.880
You are a veteran criminal investigator.
What's wrong with you?

21:29.880 --> 21:31.590
Exactly. Don't you know the rules?

21:31.590 --> 21:33.110
You're lecturing me?

21:34.000 --> 21:35.960
Dan, what is this? I'm hungry.

21:36.250 --> 21:37.250
Let me have some.

21:38.750 --> 21:39.480
It's so good.

21:41.240 --> 21:43.440
You're usually a very calm person.

21:43.440 --> 21:45.570
Why are you acting so strangely today?

21:45.880 --> 21:47.160
I'm not.

21:47.680 --> 21:48.510
Don't you think

21:48.510 --> 21:50.550
that today's operation was very strange?

21:50.550 --> 21:51.680
Don't you guys think

21:51.710 --> 21:52.920
that everything felt wrong?

21:52.920 --> 21:54.920
Wrong? What's wrong with you?

21:54.980 --> 21:55.790
Are you hungry?

21:55.790 --> 21:56.240
Yes.

21:56.240 --> 21:57.460
You're even eating
a pregnant woman's food.

21:57.460 --> 21:59.590
Let's go. I'll take you out
for a late-night snack.

21:59.590 --> 22:00.550
Are you guys coming?

22:00.550 --> 22:01.510
-Yes.
-Yes.

22:01.530 --> 22:03.060
Okay, my treat, but you pay.

22:03.240 --> 22:04.480
Let's go.

22:06.210 --> 22:07.160
Let me grab another handful.

22:07.160 --> 22:08.550
I'm not paying!

22:35.070 --> 22:36.200
Qi is looking for me.

22:39.680 --> 22:40.810
I am looking for you.

22:42.270 --> 22:43.830
Taidong Bridge in Luotang Town.

22:43.830 --> 22:45.360
Do you know what's going on?

22:46.200 --> 22:46.960
Where?

22:47.240 --> 22:50.000
Taidong Bridge, Luotang Town.

22:50.310 --> 22:52.000
The police busted a deal there

22:52.000 --> 22:53.110
and caught them red-handed.

22:53.110 --> 22:55.070
They said they caught three of your men.

22:55.070 --> 22:56.030
My men?

22:57.510 --> 22:58.750
I don't have any men.

23:00.550 --> 23:02.010
Where did you get the news?

23:04.310 --> 23:06.550
Is someone using us

23:06.550 --> 23:07.880
to sell their own goods?

23:09.330 --> 23:11.200
I only know Cheng went to a deal today,

23:11.200 --> 23:13.200
but he didn't go to that place at all.

23:13.200 --> 23:14.830
If the police want to investigate,
let them.

23:14.830 --> 23:16.440
I'm not taking the blame for this.

23:16.440 --> 23:18.510
It definitely has nothing to do with me.

23:18.510 --> 23:19.790
It better be.

23:30.890 --> 23:31.550
Qi.

23:32.880 --> 23:34.440
Yes, we're together.

23:37.310 --> 23:38.030
It's Qi.

23:43.270 --> 23:45.200
It's pitch black. I can't see crap.

23:48.430 --> 23:49.200
Qi.

23:49.400 --> 23:51.000
Why is your phone turned off?

23:56.680 --> 23:58.240
It ran out of battery.

23:58.750 --> 24:01.480
Did everything go smoothly
on the way to and back?

24:01.510 --> 24:02.710
It was pretty smooth.

24:02.920 --> 24:05.350
Have you been to
Taidong Bridge in Luotang Town?

24:05.350 --> 24:07.350
Taidong Bridge in Luotang Town?

24:07.830 --> 24:08.790
Where is that?

24:09.110 --> 24:10.840
You haven't been there, right?

24:11.880 --> 24:12.510
No.

24:13.070 --> 24:14.790
Okay, be careful on the road.

25:04.590 --> 25:06.820
October 13th.

25:08.590 --> 25:09.960
Seven to zero.

25:10.790 --> 25:11.590
Seven to zero.

25:12.480 --> 25:13.480
Sixty-three.

25:15.240 --> 25:16.000
Six.

25:16.000 --> 25:16.960
Three.

25:27.400 --> 25:29.480
Jinyuan Farmers' Market?

25:38.930 --> 25:39.650
Chief Tan.

25:40.440 --> 25:41.440
Professor Jiang.

25:42.510 --> 25:43.550
Your plan...

25:45.510 --> 25:46.710
was very successful.

25:47.480 --> 25:48.240
Jiang Cheng

25:48.750 --> 25:51.010
arranged another meeting, as expected.

25:58.040 --> 26:01.370
Longwan chickens!
Freshly slaughtered Longwan chickens!

26:01.480 --> 26:03.740
Freshly slaughtered Longwan chickens!

26:05.300 --> 26:05.960
Here you go.

26:05.960 --> 26:06.890
Okay, thank you.

26:06.920 --> 26:08.030
Come again if it's good.

26:08.030 --> 26:08.480
Okay.

26:42.790 --> 26:43.350
Cheng.

26:45.310 --> 26:46.110
Almost ready.

26:47.200 --> 26:47.920
I know.

26:56.160 --> 26:56.750
Here.

27:01.650 --> 27:03.480
You guys go ahead. I'm going over there.

27:03.480 --> 27:04.610
Where are you going?

27:05.200 --> 27:08.000
I'll get some good stuff
so I can show off my skills.

27:26.000 --> 27:27.650
Fresh Longwan chicken.

27:28.930 --> 27:30.550
Been waiting for you for a while.

27:30.550 --> 27:31.680
Why are you here too?

27:31.750 --> 27:33.160
I was here last time.

27:34.160 --> 27:35.060
You want one?

27:38.440 --> 27:39.030
This one.

27:39.030 --> 27:39.830
Sure thing.

27:40.310 --> 27:42.230
What happened
at Taidong Bridge in Luotang Town?

27:42.230 --> 27:43.150
Nothing.

27:43.960 --> 27:46.550
Arrested everyone
who needed to be arrested for you.

27:46.550 --> 27:47.610
From Luotang Town.

27:48.720 --> 27:51.350
Don't worry, I'll clean it all up for you.

27:51.680 --> 27:53.060
Come, clean it up.

27:59.640 --> 28:01.160
You guys load the stuff.
I'll go take a look.

28:01.160 --> 28:01.490
Okay.

28:02.030 --> 28:02.960
I'll go with you.

28:05.480 --> 28:07.030
Hurry up, I'm in a rush.

28:07.640 --> 28:08.720
Then pay first.

28:09.310 --> 28:09.880
How much?

28:09.930 --> 28:10.800
Eighty-five.

28:12.710 --> 28:13.600
Cash?

28:17.750 --> 28:18.240
Here.

28:18.460 --> 28:20.260
You guys are in for a treat today.

28:30.170 --> 28:31.070
You're in the way, don't you know?

28:31.070 --> 28:32.550
What do you mean I'm in the way?
You bumped into me.

28:32.550 --> 28:33.590
You two think you're right?
What do you mean?

28:33.590 --> 28:34.240
Who bumped into you?

28:34.240 --> 28:35.830
We were walking normally.
You pushed the cart over.

28:35.830 --> 28:37.400
We were pushing the cart normally.
Are you blind?

28:37.400 --> 28:38.160
Alright, alright.

28:38.160 --> 28:39.110
Hurry up and clean it up.

28:39.110 --> 28:39.790
Stop arguing.

28:39.790 --> 28:40.720
What can you do to me?

28:40.720 --> 28:42.590
Stop arguing! Let's settle this properly.

28:42.590 --> 28:44.120
How do you want to settle it?

28:45.960 --> 28:47.790
Put that away first.
I'll pay you, alright?

28:47.790 --> 28:49.920
You pay? Pay me 500 or 600.

28:50.070 --> 28:50.550
Hurry up.

28:50.550 --> 28:51.950
Give him 50 and it's done.

28:51.950 --> 28:53.230
What? Fifty?

28:53.350 --> 28:54.440
What, is 50 not enough?

28:54.440 --> 28:55.700
You think I'm a beggar?

28:55.800 --> 28:57.260
Alright, we'll pick it up.

28:57.790 --> 28:58.270
Leave it there.

28:58.270 --> 28:59.240
Alright.

28:59.440 --> 29:00.960
I've never seen people like this, really.

29:00.960 --> 29:02.310
I've never seen someone like you either,

29:02.310 --> 29:03.590
walking without looking.

29:03.590 --> 29:05.120
Extorting people, really.

29:19.530 --> 29:20.010
Cheng,

29:20.120 --> 29:21.270
are you going to make braised chicken?

29:21.270 --> 29:23.440
Want another one at a discount?

29:23.660 --> 29:24.180
No need.

29:37.750 --> 29:39.550
Good thing Mr. Wan reacted fast.

29:53.370 --> 29:53.970
Zhao Ping.

29:54.480 --> 29:55.200
Liu Liang.

29:56.670 --> 29:57.700
You two leave immediately

29:57.700 --> 29:58.760
and go to Jingzhou.

29:59.240 --> 30:00.240
The Crime Research Lab

30:00.240 --> 30:01.350
is re-examining

30:01.590 --> 30:02.390
the 8/17 Case,

30:02.640 --> 30:03.570
the serial case,

30:03.720 --> 30:04.310
and

30:04.640 --> 30:06.440
the Jingang Wharf's case files.

30:06.850 --> 30:09.510
They will give us a guide
for the investigation.

30:09.880 --> 30:10.590
You guys go

30:11.030 --> 30:13.090
and find Director Wang Pengze first.

30:13.310 --> 30:14.440
Your main task is to assist him

30:14.440 --> 30:15.770
and explain what we know

30:16.000 --> 30:17.350
to them.

30:17.680 --> 30:19.640
Call me anytime
if you are unclear about anything.

30:19.640 --> 30:19.990
Yes.

30:20.920 --> 30:22.250
After you get the files,

30:22.310 --> 30:23.440
bring them back to me

30:24.020 --> 30:24.820
immediately.

30:25.240 --> 30:25.840
Remember,

30:26.720 --> 30:27.400
no mailing.

30:27.510 --> 30:28.000
Yes.

30:28.920 --> 30:29.520
Chief Tan,

30:29.750 --> 30:31.440
how long will we be gone this time?

30:31.440 --> 30:32.970
Probably two or three days.

30:33.500 --> 30:34.960
Bring some fresh clothes.

30:34.960 --> 30:35.440
Yes.

30:35.480 --> 30:35.920
Here.

30:37.270 --> 30:38.030
Hand this

30:38.400 --> 30:40.060
to Director Wang personally.

30:40.550 --> 30:42.280
The document is confidential.

30:42.440 --> 30:44.180
Guard it with your life.

30:44.310 --> 30:44.880
Yes.

30:46.090 --> 30:47.350
After giving it to him,

30:47.730 --> 30:48.900
give me a call.

30:48.920 --> 30:49.510
Okay.

30:50.160 --> 30:50.720
Go ahead.

30:51.070 --> 30:51.590
Yes.

31:25.240 --> 31:26.040
Director Guo.

31:27.510 --> 31:28.070
Yes.

31:29.550 --> 31:30.950
There's major progress.

31:38.020 --> 31:38.820
You know what,

31:39.780 --> 31:41.310
smelling this mountain air

31:41.440 --> 31:42.640
is quite refreshing.

31:43.770 --> 31:44.790
It smells like medicine.

31:44.790 --> 31:45.790
I don't like it.

31:56.390 --> 31:58.640
[Real-time Data Analysis
of the Public Security Bureau]

31:57.600 --> 31:59.200
They've entered Kuangshan.

32:01.880 --> 32:03.920
Many areas in Kuangshan
are primary forests.

32:03.920 --> 32:05.510
Following this route up,

32:05.600 --> 32:06.510
the only habitable places

32:06.510 --> 32:08.530
are Maohe Village and Yatou Village.

32:08.530 --> 32:10.410
Neither village has large populations,

32:10.410 --> 32:12.270
only 40 to 50 households in total.

32:12.950 --> 32:14.380
Within a three-kilometer radius,

32:14.380 --> 32:15.930
there are
six medicinal herb processing plants

32:15.930 --> 32:17.390
and some small workshops.

32:18.890 --> 32:20.350
They are producing drugs.

32:20.480 --> 32:23.680
A pharmaceutical factory
is the best cover for a drug lab.

33:01.370 --> 33:02.660
They changed from driving to walking,

33:02.660 --> 33:04.060
it should be around here.

33:04.840 --> 33:06.120
It really is the medicine factory?

33:06.120 --> 33:07.120
Kuangshan West,

33:08.370 --> 33:10.170
Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory.

33:17.450 --> 33:21.230
[Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory]

33:30.170 --> 33:31.490
The superiors have approved

33:31.490 --> 33:33.250
the decision to conduct

33:33.270 --> 33:34.880
secret investigations

33:35.030 --> 33:36.480
and strike operations against

33:36.480 --> 33:37.640
the possible drug factory
in Kuangshan West.

33:37.640 --> 33:40.350
This operation will be jointly led by
Deputy Commander Liu Zishan

33:40.350 --> 33:42.070
of the Provincial
Criminal Investigation Department,

33:42.070 --> 33:44.070
and Deputy Director Guo Jianmin

33:44.070 --> 33:45.160
of the municipal police station.

33:45.160 --> 33:46.820
The municipal bureau
will set up the command center.

33:46.820 --> 33:48.480
We're a surveillance ops team formed by

33:48.480 --> 33:49.510
the CIB Nancheng Branch,

33:49.510 --> 33:50.510
the municipal SWAT team,

33:50.510 --> 33:52.510
and the anti-drug team.

33:52.700 --> 33:54.740
Deploy and set up control at 3 P.M.

34:09.650 --> 34:10.960
Reporting to the Command Center.

34:10.960 --> 34:12.480
According to the reconnaissance,

34:12.480 --> 34:13.760
Yatou Pharmaceutical Factory

34:13.760 --> 34:15.760
has three main factory buildings inside.

34:15.760 --> 34:17.719
Each is about 800 square meters.

34:17.920 --> 34:19.800
The largest one is three stories high.

34:19.800 --> 34:21.590
Since they evaded previous inspections,

34:21.590 --> 34:24.400
there should be underground levels
and secret passages.

34:24.400 --> 34:26.389
Based on the topography of Kuangshan,

34:26.389 --> 34:28.090
the technical department has built

34:28.090 --> 34:29.590
a digital model of the factory.

34:29.590 --> 34:30.940
We have formulated corresponding

34:30.940 --> 34:32.610
attack and defense strategies and routes.

34:32.610 --> 34:35.060
Now transmitting to all units.

34:38.260 --> 34:38.870
Received.

34:39.280 --> 34:40.969
Let us know if you need anything.

34:40.969 --> 34:43.800
The Command Center will fully support you.

34:43.840 --> 34:44.570
Understood.

34:44.670 --> 34:46.600
We will act at the designated time.

34:47.110 --> 34:47.969
Pair of threes.

34:49.150 --> 34:50.400
Pair of threes...

34:51.400 --> 34:52.110
Pass.

34:52.190 --> 34:53.150
Pass, right?

34:53.800 --> 34:55.420
Nine, ten, jack, queen, king.

34:55.420 --> 34:56.030
Hello,

34:56.030 --> 34:58.090
the number you dialed is powered off.

34:58.590 --> 34:59.550
I knew you had to pass.

34:59.550 --> 35:00.070
King.

35:01.480 --> 35:02.110
Anyone?

35:02.710 --> 35:03.400
Ace.

35:03.960 --> 35:04.630
Two.

35:06.400 --> 35:07.510
Cheng, where are you going?

35:07.510 --> 35:09.110
I'm going out. You guys play.

35:21.850 --> 35:23.310
I need to see Old Scorpion.

35:29.210 --> 35:30.500
What's the rush?

35:38.170 --> 35:39.290
I want to see Old Scorpion.

35:39.290 --> 35:40.770
Aren't you Old Scorpion?

35:42.150 --> 35:42.840
Boss He,

35:43.190 --> 35:44.630
don't mess with me.

35:46.410 --> 35:48.270
I'm looking for Old Scorpion too.

35:48.720 --> 35:50.380
I haven't been able to see him.

35:50.810 --> 35:52.940
Message Qiu Ye if you need anything.

35:53.540 --> 35:55.220
I did, but she didn't reply.

35:57.670 --> 35:59.230
Maybe she's

35:59.230 --> 36:00.670
in another warehouse

36:00.670 --> 36:01.960
without any signal.

36:03.200 --> 36:04.600
I'll go find her with you?

36:05.590 --> 36:06.280
Forget it.

36:06.360 --> 36:07.360
Too much trouble.

36:07.590 --> 36:08.150
Cheng.

36:10.360 --> 36:11.880
If you're free,

36:12.630 --> 36:13.510
come to my place

36:14.010 --> 36:15.010
for a drink.

36:16.670 --> 36:17.150
Sure.

36:24.670 --> 36:25.400
Cheng.

36:27.400 --> 36:28.670
We haven't had

36:29.150 --> 36:30.920
a calm and quiet talk like this

36:30.940 --> 36:31.770
in a while.

36:33.400 --> 36:35.000
You look tired.

36:35.800 --> 36:36.550
Why?

36:37.590 --> 36:38.360
Stressed?

36:38.960 --> 36:39.920
I'm fine.

36:40.760 --> 36:41.760
It's just that

36:42.000 --> 36:43.660
I haven't been sleeping well.

36:43.800 --> 36:44.600
Thanks, Boss.

36:49.880 --> 36:50.810
Do you regret it?

36:51.890 --> 36:53.200
Regret trying so hard

36:53.770 --> 36:55.370
to climb up the ladder?

36:56.880 --> 36:57.630
Regret?

37:00.360 --> 37:01.690
I regret a lot of things.

37:03.510 --> 37:05.400
You can only be loyal

37:05.880 --> 37:07.230
when there's no way out.

37:08.590 --> 37:09.990
We all went through this.

37:10.400 --> 37:11.070
You are

37:12.150 --> 37:13.560
still too young.

37:14.190 --> 37:14.670
Come on.

37:23.070 --> 37:23.710
Boss He,

37:24.200 --> 37:25.660
what new product are they researching

37:25.660 --> 37:26.910
so tirelessly?

37:32.590 --> 37:33.320
Cheng,

37:33.670 --> 37:35.080
I told you before

37:35.920 --> 37:39.050
that Old Scorpion's biggest trait
is being mysterious.

37:39.230 --> 37:40.070
So,

37:41.150 --> 37:42.520
I never ask questions.

37:46.280 --> 37:47.340
Where is everyone?

37:50.230 --> 37:51.290
Where is everyone?

37:52.070 --> 37:53.510
They all ran away, right?

38:27.350 --> 38:28.480
Qi is looking for me.

38:36.510 --> 38:37.190
Boss He,

38:37.690 --> 38:38.860
stop pretending.

38:39.130 --> 38:40.450
When did they leave?

38:40.470 --> 38:41.430
You must know.

38:45.440 --> 38:46.300
Where are they?

38:47.690 --> 38:48.650
I'm asking you!

38:48.760 --> 38:49.620
Where are they?

38:49.710 --> 38:50.840
I don't know either.

38:52.000 --> 38:53.790
I was just told to guard here

38:54.030 --> 38:55.400
and not let anyone in.

38:55.650 --> 38:56.710
When did this happen?

38:56.710 --> 38:58.310
The night before yesterday.

39:00.480 --> 39:02.480
Looks like they left a long time ago.

39:02.480 --> 39:03.440
But it's fine.

39:04.030 --> 39:04.630
Boss He,

39:05.150 --> 39:06.550
you being here works too.

39:06.630 --> 39:07.630
I just want to ask,

39:07.680 --> 39:08.590
when will you pay me

39:08.590 --> 39:09.800
the three million in commission?

39:09.800 --> 39:10.440
What?

39:10.580 --> 39:12.140
Qi made a deal with me

39:12.160 --> 39:14.210
that as long as I
brought that cop back alive,

39:14.210 --> 39:16.470
he'd pay me three million in commission.

39:16.740 --> 39:18.140
That cop is dead.

39:18.230 --> 39:18.590
Dead?

39:19.880 --> 39:21.270
If he's dead, then you guys killed him.

39:21.270 --> 39:22.110
Not us!

39:22.250 --> 39:24.160
He was alive when we brought him back.

39:24.160 --> 39:25.490
He was still breathing!

39:26.590 --> 39:27.150
Fine.

39:28.190 --> 39:29.720
Then wait for Qi to come back

39:30.520 --> 39:31.070
and have him pay you.

39:31.070 --> 39:31.960
Wait for him?

39:31.960 --> 39:33.840
Do you think I'm an idiot? Look around!

39:33.840 --> 39:35.400
They all ran away!

39:37.190 --> 39:38.710
Calm down.

39:38.840 --> 39:40.510
Once Qi comes back,

39:40.510 --> 39:42.280
I'll ask him what the plan is.

39:42.280 --> 39:43.590
Your next step

39:43.590 --> 39:44.710
has nothing to do with me.

39:44.710 --> 39:46.000
You weren't telling the truth anyway.

39:46.000 --> 39:47.000
I thought

39:47.060 --> 39:48.280
after the Jingang Wharf matter
was settled,

39:48.280 --> 39:50.010
I could easily get my money.

39:50.030 --> 39:51.110
But now?

39:51.110 --> 39:52.590
You made a mess of it.

39:52.760 --> 39:54.590
You guys caused so much trouble!

39:59.510 --> 40:00.110
Bro.

40:01.570 --> 40:03.900
Things didn't go as smoothly
as you think.

40:03.960 --> 40:04.590
Boss He.

40:08.550 --> 40:10.210
Every industry has its rules.

40:10.360 --> 40:12.190
My men and I risked our lives here

40:12.600 --> 40:14.460
just for that commission, right?

40:14.630 --> 40:16.880
Now, you can't let him live it up

40:16.960 --> 40:18.630
while you screw us out of our money.

40:18.630 --> 40:19.510
No way!

40:23.800 --> 40:25.330
You want to run away, right?

40:26.590 --> 40:27.250
No problem.

40:28.230 --> 40:28.960
Come with me.

40:40.960 --> 40:42.220
Let's go get the money.

40:47.400 --> 40:48.460
What are you doing?

40:48.750 --> 40:49.280
Let go.

40:51.110 --> 40:51.840
Let go.

41:14.300 --> 41:15.160
See that?

41:15.800 --> 41:16.760
They all left.

41:17.800 --> 41:19.060
This kind of dirty work

41:19.880 --> 41:21.280
was left for us to handle.

41:22.150 --> 41:23.750
They're on the same side.

41:26.170 --> 41:26.770
Cheng,

41:28.190 --> 41:30.250
you better just follow me from now on.

41:31.440 --> 41:33.400
We are the only two left now.

41:34.980 --> 41:36.240
Two wanted criminals.

41:37.110 --> 41:37.890
Two...

41:37.920 --> 41:39.110
watchdogs.

41:41.280 --> 41:42.080
What's wrong?

41:42.840 --> 41:43.630
Regret it?

41:44.400 --> 41:46.150
It's too late to regret now.

41:47.550 --> 41:48.750
Sorry to trouble you,

41:48.770 --> 41:49.770
but get rid of him.

42:09.150 --> 42:10.360
Team 1 and Team 2,

42:10.840 --> 42:12.320
go up the mountain to Position 1 now.

42:12.320 --> 42:13.310
Team 1 copies.

42:24.880 --> 42:25.920
Surveillance team,

42:25.920 --> 42:26.920
stake out closely

42:27.030 --> 42:28.560
and watch out for sentries.

42:28.630 --> 42:29.230
Copy that.

43:04.840 --> 43:05.440
All right.

43:05.630 --> 43:06.320
Let's bury him here.
